transcript_analysis.full_transcript: It's a new month, so that means new beauty at Mecca.  Hi, my name is Mandy and I love trying new beauty products.  So let's get to know some of the latest drops that have just landed.  First, we have Kits Workout Wash.  It's perfect for summer because it's designed to rinse away your sweat and sweat.  Another great cleanser for summer is Touches The Deep Cleanse.  It gently exfoliates your face, leaving it feeling soft and smooth.  Moving on to makeup, we have the Brow Guru Microchip Pencil from Mecca Max,  which is so easy to use.  For the face, we have the new Inner Good Light Palette by Mecca Cosmetica.  These powders work seamlessly together to help soften, define and enhance your skin.  It is absolutely stunning.  For the lips, we have this set from Clinique that is exclusive to Mecca,  containing two black honey lip products that compliments any skin tone.  And finally, F.L.U.R.E. have this limited mist duo for Valentine's Day.  Inspired by Berry Matcha Latte, these smell incredible on the skin.  Thank you so much for watching.  Head in-store or online to discover all the new arrivals that have just landed.
